  "subject": "[SECURITY] Add reporting page for the versions tests",
  "commit_message": "[SECURITY] Add reporting page for the versions tests\n\nSo far the results of versions are a json or a log file\nIt is easier to understand the status via a html reporting page[1]\n\nThis patch is the first one of a serie\nas versions shall be launched differently and reporting called at the end of the test\nto generate the reporting page\nMeanwhile it can be used manually\nthe needed inputs are:\n- the seccom recommended list\n- a waiver file (to exclude filebeat)\n\nIssue-ID: TEST-304\n\n[1]: https://logs.onap.org/onap-integration/weekly/onap_weekly_pod4_master/02-11-2021_22-02/security/versions/versions/\n\nSigned-off-by: mrichomme <morgan.richomme@orange.com>\nChange-Id: I9ec8a565d754b208fb1eac77561f0462e7512f95\n",
